longBusinessSummary: Wee Hur Holdings Ltd., an investment holding company, engages in general building and civil engineering construction business in Singapore and Australia. It operates through Building Construction, Worker's Dormitory, Property Development, PBSA, Fund Management, PBSA Operation, and Other Investment segments. The company constructs various projects, which include residential, commercial, industrial, institutional, religious, restoration and conservation projects for private and public sectors. It also provides conducive living environment, including commercial and non-commercial amenities, such as indoor recreational and gymnasium, canteens, minimarts, retail shops, and outdoor game courts, as well as multi-purpose, TV, and reading rooms for foreign workers from construction, marine, process, and manufacturing industries. In addition, the company develops and sells residential, industrial, and mixed-used properties; and manages student accommodation that comprise reservation and sales, marketing, customer service, property management, and business development. Further, it offers fund management and venture capital services; leases non-financial intangible assets comprising patents, trademarks, brand names, etc.; builds and operates workers' dormitories; and leases office and commercial properties. The company was founded in 1980 and is based in Singapore.
